      "type": "text",
      "name": "help_text",
      "value": "Present a group of three to six problems all at once for your students to sort from easiest to hardest. Discuss the reasoning behind the sorting order, and then discuss the methods they used to do the problems. Where in the sequence did students stop being able to do the problems in their heads and why.",
      "parameter_list": "icon_src: help; style:navigation"
    },
    {
